menu "SDF Zigbee"

config SDF_ZIGBEE_ENABLE
    bool "Enable Zigbee functionality"
    default y
    help
        Enable the Zigbee stack and Zigbee-facing application behavior.
        Disable this to run the device without Zigbee and allow the power
        manager to treat the device as standalone when idle.

config SDF_ZIGBEE_SLEEP_THRESHOLD_MS
    int "Minimum idle time before Zigbee sleep (ms)"
    range 10 5000
    default 20
    help
        The Zigbee stack will only enter sleep if the idle window
        is longer than this threshold. Low values save more power
        but increase wake transitions.

config SDF_ZIGBEE_SLEEP_ENABLE
    bool "Enable Zigbee sleepy end-device mode"
    default y
    help
        Enable light-sleep for the Zigbee radio between check-in polls.
        Requires CONFIG_PM_ENABLE and CONFIG_FREERTOS_USE_TICKLESS_IDLE.

endmenu
